text:
BREAKING: The Chinese city of Wuhan, the first to record human cases of #COVID19, has banned the consumption of ALL wildlife for five years.

HSI welcomes this move but encourages Wuhan to implement a permanent and comprehensive ban on the wildlife trade. https://t.co/SFbZqc1i1w
